.TH pif-config-verbose-set 1  "pif-config-verbose-set " 
.SH NAME
pif\-config\-verbose\-set \- Persist a verbosity level to the config file
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBpif\-config\-verbose\-set\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fILEVEL\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Persist a verbosity level to the config file
.PP
Levels:
.PP
1 — errors and warnings only 2 — normal output (default) 3 — detailed / debug output
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
<\fILEVEL\fR>
Verbosity level to persist (1–3)
